            <p class="content-box-discription mb-1">2.1.4 As a general rule, the Company will not disclose personally identifiable information except when the Company is required or permitted per customer agreement, law (including pursuant to national security of law enforcement requirements) or otherwise, such as when the Company believes in good faith that the law requires disclosure or other circumstances outlined in this Privacy Policy require or permit disclosure.</p>

            <ul>
