            <p class="content-box-discription mb-1">2.1.8 The Company utilizes a self-assessment approach to support compliance with this Privacy Policy.</p>

            <ul>
                <li class="mb-1">
                    <p class="content-box-discription mb-0">The Company periodically verifies that related policies are accurate, comprehensive for the information intended to be covered, prominently displayed, implemented, and are in conformity with the principles of this Privacy Policy.</p>
